      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PHOENIX AMELIA (1) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 30.67 beating Moet Magic. Has good early burn and is suited drawn on the inside. Expected to be right there at the finish again. VALIDATE (4) shapes well after a sharp run last time, finishing second in a Free For All at this track in 25.31. Top win latest and can measure up again. SHE'S PEAKIN' (8) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (34.69) at Q Parklands. Form here excellent including two wins. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to be in this for a long way. ART OF DECEPTION (2) won last start in very good time. Big chance on that form.",
